title: BRIEF-TXT e-solutions sees Q3 2015 revenues up by 10 pct to EUR 14.0 mln
text:
BRIEF-TXT e-solutions sees Q3 2015 revenues up by 10 pct to EUR 14.0 mln 
Oct 14 TXT e-solutions SpA : 
* Sees Q3 2015 revenues of about 14.0 million euros ($16.0 million), up 10 percent year on year 
* Reports 9-months new orders for 46.9 million euros, up 18.8 percent year on year
